 time and by topic than between the two worlds. Both worlds also saw the development of ever more sophisticated justifications. Amid the increasing complexity of justifications, a particular kind of reasoning emerged: that good outcomes are more important than upholding rules for their own sake.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aIdols and imagesxWorshipxReligious aspectsxChristianity. 0aIdols and imagesxWorshipxReligious aspectsxIslam. 0aInterest (Islamic law). 0aSinxChristianity. 0aSinxIslam. 0aSodomyxReligious aspectsxChristianity. 0aSodomyxReligious aspectsxIslam. 0aUsury laws (Canon law). 4aComparative World History. 4aIdolatry. 4aSodomy. 4aUsury. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology of Religion.2bisacsh  aSodomy.  acomparative world history.  aconsequentialism.  aidolatry.  alegal pluralism.  ausury.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2023 Englishz978311131914808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2023z9783111318226oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831112186250 cprintz978311121590740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783111218014zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783111218014zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783111218014/original  a978-3-11-131914-8 EBOOK PACKAGE Law 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-G